Global Automotive Active Engine Mount Market Insights
Automotive Active Engine Mount Market size was valued at USD 2.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 4.1 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Automotive Active Engine Mount Market Overview
The global automotive active engine mount market is valued at approximately USD 5.3 billion in 2024 and is expected to reach USD 8.2 billion by 2030, with a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 8.5%. Active engine mounts are vital components that help reduce engine vibrations, improve vehicle performance, and ensure a smoother driving experience. The growing demand for advanced automotive technologies, along with rising consumer preferences for better ride comfort and noise reduction, is fueling the market growth. Additionally, stringent government regulations for reducing emissions and noise pollution are contributing to market expansion.

